Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.93,0:06:37.73,EDJP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}You are a shy boy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.09,0:06:41.19,EDJP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}今日こそ何か
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.41,0:06:44.21,EDJP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}言って欲しいな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:48.99,EDJP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}ポピーの帰り道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.19,0:06:54.19,EDJP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}そんなに見ても
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.53,0:07:02.17,EDJP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}だめよ 私から告白したくないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.41,0:07:07.35,EDJP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}急に 立ち止まったら
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:10.45,EDJP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}それが 切っ掛けでキス?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:17.19,EDJP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}無理ね あなたは弱気なshy boy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.73,0:07:21.07,EDJP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}永遠に続くみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.07,0:07:25.27,EDJP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}花咲けるこの時が
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.77,0:07:30.65,EDJP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}二人きり焦れったいけれど スきよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.89,0:07:34.05,EDJP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}夕焼けを背に受けて
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.19,0:07:37.99,EDJP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}あなたから囁いて
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:44.89,EDJP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}「君が運命の天使だよ」と
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.35,0:07:49.09,EDJP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}それで許してあげる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.09,0:06:41.19,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}今天也有很多话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.41,0:06:44.21,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}想要告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:48.99,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}孩童时代的回家路上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.19,0:06:54.19,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}就算你那样看着我
